{"tid":548902,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"薯片教做人︰好打得仲要有武德","createTime":"2018-02-03T06:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T13:45:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8591e3328cf8232fa62c79e2f6136292ceeaa84a","tid":548902,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:03:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180203/20294149\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F20294149&d=uX%2BhsQGbvnpEibZKVEWEKUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=8ff625fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F20294149&h=c1761e76\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180203/20294149</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n薯片教做人︰好打得仲要有武德 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇見一排嘅前財爺薯片叔曾俊華，噚日現身時代廣場，為鳳冠師傅陳國源嘅展覽做開幕嘉賓。近排熱廚房高度升溫，無官一身輕嘅薯片叔卻風騷不已，喺活動上大講武德，語帶雙關話做人除咗要「好打得」，仲要有武德，即係忠義仁勇、尊師重道等等，而且最重要「虛心求教」，唔通隔空向前同事、特首林鄭放話？<br />\n<br />\n薯片叔仲借成名多年嘅陳國源師傅，年輕時得到師母贊助30大元創業，以及漢朝大將韓信都係因為一飯之恩而成大器為例子，勸勉成年人畀多啲機會年輕人，唔知薯片叔呢番話，一眾AO後輩、尤其擔任選舉主任嗰幾位，會唔會特別有感受？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180203/large/03lp2p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180203%2Flarge%2F03lp2p01.jpg&h=af2e66fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾俊華噚日為鳳冠師傅陳國源展覽做嘉賓，席間大談武德。 <br />\n謝榮耀攝"},{"pid":"3ccb289a2b6f9ce2145ae9e38021d6c7fcca2fdf","tid":548902,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:06:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08c1e81255dbdee43fe890e9241f6b825cdd859d","tid":548902,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:09:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"175500229b02f5e2488a43eeb256678d9ce2c46d","tid":548902,"uid":7699,